  <div class="main main-raised">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-description text-center">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8 ml-auto mr-auto">
            <h5 class="description">While we absolutely love productivity software, we believe productivity, in general, is broken. There's just too many tools to keep track of, too many things in entirely separate ecosystems. There has to be a
              better way to work - that's why we created ProjectManager, first an internal tool, now as a way to fulfill our vision of making the world more productive.</h5>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-services features-2">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8 ml-auto mr-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="title">Our Mission</h2>
            <h5 class="description">Eventually, our goal is to have all work live in ProjectHub- thereby making people more productive and giving back at least 20% of time to dedicate to other things. One app to replace them all. </h5>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="info info-horizontal">
              <div class="icon icon-rose">
                <i class="material-icons">gesture</i>
              </div>
              <div class="description">
                <h4 class="info-title">1. Clear communication & collaboration</h4>
                <p>Its really important to communicate effectively and its really tedious to communicate through different platforms. The idea is to build virtual teams that feel connected and stay in touch regularly. </p>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="info info-horizontal">
              <div class="icon icon-rose">
                <i class="material-icons">build</i>
              </div>
              <div class="description">
                <h4 class="info-title">2. Data Centralization</h4>
                <p>With the current lockdown context, organizations have no other option than to centralize the information (communication, work sheets, reports, documents). Without a centralized information system, there can no longer be proper
                  project management..</p>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="info info-horizontal">
              <div class="icon icon-rose">
                <i class="material-icons">mode_edit</i>
              </div>
              <div class="description">
                <h4 class="info-title">3. Efficient monitoring</h4>
                <p>More than ever, monitoring is key to efficient project management. With a good data centralization tool, you should be able to achieve efficient reporting. List of tasks can be assigned by the ProjectHub to all members of the team.
                  No one can claim they haven't seen task assignments or didn't know something was due.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
